<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrīśakavatsarē rasaviyat bāhukṣamāsaṁ
<lb n="2" break="no"/>mmitē dīpārtthaṁ kamaṭhākṛtē rbhagavatō bhūtyai paraṁ cakṣiṇa
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> dhēnūnaṁ varapaṁcaviṁśatimādādā(ṁ)caṁdratārāgaṇaṁ śrīmānarjja
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ma śeṭṭiraṁgaḍipatirḍḍaṁkkōḷagōtrōt bhavaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śakavaruṣaṁbu
<lb n="5" break="no"/>lu 1206 nēṁṭi riṣabhasaṁkraṁtināṁḍu Oḍḍavādi ciṁgama śeṭṭi ma
<lb n="6" break="no"/>numaṁḍu bhīmu śēṭṭi koḍuku Aṁgaḍināyakuṁḍaina Arjjama
<lb n="7" break="no"/>śeṭṭi tanaku nāyuṣkāmārtthamugānu śrīkūrmmanāthuniki nācaṁdra
<lb n="8" break="no"/>rkkamugānu dīpamu celluṭakunu peṭṭinā mōdālu 25 kaṁcudīpa da
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ṁḍu 1 visyalu 6 I darmmuvu śrīvaiṣṇamarakṣa śrīśrīśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

